00034 // returns if the value is known or not
00035 bool isNotKnown(Value v)
00036 {
00037     switch(v)
00038      {
00039             case ONE:
00040             case ZERO:
00041             case D:
00042             case DBAR:
00043             return false;
00044         
00045         default:
00046             return true;
00047      }
00048      return true;
00049 }

00052 int Translate_Value_To_Int(Value value)
00053 {
00054     switch(value)
00055     {
00056         case 0x0: 
00057             return 0;
00058         case 0xff:
00059             return 1;
00060     }
00061     return 0;

00066 /*Use only to check if value is c xor i or  cbar xor i*/
00067 Value Do_Xor(Value val1, Value val2)
00068 {
00069     Value output;
00070     Value negval1 =  (Value) (val1 != U)?(Value)(~(val1)&0xf):U;
00071     Value negval2 =  (Value) (val2 != U)?(Value)(~(val2)&0xf):U;
00072     output = (Value)((( (val1 & negval2) | (negval1 & val2)))&0xf);
00073     return output;
00074 }

00097 void Print_All_Wires(Circuit& circuit)
00098 {
00099     CIRCUIT_DFILE << "Print_All_Wires called"  << endl;
00100     // Print out the primary inputs
00101     CIRCUIT_DFILE << "Printing all the PIs "   << endl << endl;
00102     map<string,Wire*> ::iterator iter =  (circuit.PriInputs).begin();
00103 
00104     for (;iter != (circuit.PriInputs).end(); iter++)
00105     {   
00106         CIRCUIT_DFILE << setw(20) << (iter->second)->id << ":    " << (iter->second)->value << endl;
00107     }
00108 
00109 
00110     // Print out the primary outputs
00111     iter =  (circuit.PriOutputs).begin();
00112     CIRCUIT_DFILE << "Printing all POs " << endl << endl;
00113     for (;iter != (circuit.PriOutputs).end(); iter++)
00114     {   
00115         CIRCUIT_DFILE  << setw(20) << (iter->second)->id << ":    " << (iter->second)->value << endl;
00116     }
00117 
00118 
00119     // Print out the netlist
00120     iter =  (circuit.Netlist).begin();
00121     CIRCUIT_DFILE << "Printing out the netlist " << endl << endl;
00122     for (;iter != (circuit.Netlist).end(); iter++)
00123     {   
00124         CIRCUIT_DFILE << setw(20) << (iter->second)->id << ":    " << (iter->second)->value << endl;
00125     }
00126 
00127     CIRCUIT_DFILE <<  endl << endl;
00128 }
